# Normalize all text to LF in the repo and in the working tree. This project is
# developed on WSL; forcing CRLF for .cs (the .NET-on-Windows convention) would
# fight `dotnet format` and the LF working tree. Line endings do not affect the
# compiled assembly, so LF is used uniformly for a frictionless WSL workflow.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets: never normalize.
*.dll binary
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.zip binary

# The XML doc that ships beside the SDK reference DLL is binary-ish; keep verbatim.
src/FanControl.LianLi/dlls/FanControl.Plugins.xml -text

*.sln merge=union
